    <div class="digital-participation callout">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="mdc-layout-grid">
                <div class="mdc-layout-grid__inner">
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-9-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-5-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <h2>Tackling digital exclusion in Scotland</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <a href="https://digitalparticipation.scot">
                            <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/scvo-cms/scvo-cms-content/images/digital/charter-logo.png" class="pull-right v-margin" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mdc-layout-grid__inner">
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/scvo-cms/scvo-cms-content/images/digital/Main-Hero-RGB-04-wee.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <div class="mdc-card">
                            <section class="mdc-card__primary">
                                <h3>What's the issue?</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    One in five people lack basic digital skills.
                                    Confidence, access and affordability can also prevent people benefiting from being online.
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://digitalparticipation.scot/skill-up">Understand the skills</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://digitalparticipation.scot/resources/reports">Read the research</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <div class="mdc-card">
                            <section class="mdc-card__primary">
                                <h3>Get involved</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    Can you play a role in building people's confidence and basic digital skills?
                                    Can you help tackle the issues of accessibility or affordability?
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://digitalparticipation.scot/sign-up">Sign the Charter</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://digitalparticipation.scot/signatories">View signatories</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://digitalparticipation.scot/resources">Find resources</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <div class="mdc-card">
                            <section class="mdc-card__primary">
                                <h3>Get support</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    Find out more about the support we can offer to help build the skills and
                                    confidence of your workforce and people you work with.
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/participation/champions">Digital Champion Training</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/participation/charter-fund">Apply for funding</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/participation/charter-fund/projects">View projects</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="digital-evolution callout">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="mdc-layout-grid">
                <div class="mdc-layout-grid__inner">
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-12">
                        <h2>Building a digitally confident third sector</h2>
