                                <h3>What's the issue?</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    New technology and the internet has changed the way we live our lives.
                                    Has the third sector responded to this change?
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/post/2016/11/08/digital-call-to-action-third-sector-scotland">Read the Call to Action</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <div class="mdc-card">
