                                <h3>Adapt and evolve</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    Wherever you are in your digital journey, we're aiming to provide support to
                                    help you maximise the benefits and minimise the risks.
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/evolution/check-up">Digital Check-Up</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/evolution/cyber-resilience">Cyber Resilience</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/evolution/senior-leaders-programme">Leaders Programme</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="https://charitycatalogue.com">Find Digital Tools</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
                        <div class="mdc-card">
                            <section class="mdc-card__primary">
                                <h3>Digital Pioneer Case Studies</h3>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__supporting-text">
                                <p>
                                    From Facebook campaigns to Google Analytics, iConnect North East tell us what digital has to offer.
                                </p>
                            </section>
                            <section class="mdc-card__actions">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a class="mdc-card__action mdc-button mdc-button--raised" href="/digital/evolution/digital-pioneers">More case studies</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </section>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
